    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/daefb56fc73ddedf1e473619e097d187.avif?t=1735062372\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leap into the Future</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>HYPERLEAP</strong>, a single-player parkour game set in a futuristic, grid-based world where speed and agility are key to survival. Navigate through neon-lit environments using smooth parkour mechanics like wall-running, sliding, dashing, and leaping. With jump pads and moving platforms, every run feels dynamic and intense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this fast-paced adventure, different paths can be taken in some levels, adding variety and allowing you to find the fastest route to the finish line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/126fc0b8eb9d92df4f26eb9f11fc2507.poster.avif?t=1735062372\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/126fc0b8eb9d92df4f26eb9f11fc2507.webm?t=1735062372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/126fc0b8eb9d92df4f26eb9f11fc2507.mp4?t=1735062372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Challenge Awaits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>HYPERLEAP</strong>, it's not just about speed, there are enemies standing in your way. Outrun and outmaneuver hostile forces using your parkour skills and tactical thinking. While exploration is minimal, collecting scattered stars adds an extra layer of difficulty. Master the timing and precision of your movements to gather every star and complete the level at 100%. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lava pits, moving platforms, and dangerous enemies create obstacles that demand split-second decision-making and relentless forward momentum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/eef85d5e4944050eea6379771fa02852.poster.avif?t=1735062372\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/eef85d5e4944050eea6379771fa02852.webm?t=1735062372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119730/extras/eef85d5e4944050eea6379771fa02852.mp4?t=1735062372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Race Against Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time is your biggest enemy in <strong>HYPERLEAP</strong>. Each level features a built-in timer to track how quickly you can finish, pushing you to perfect your route and maximize your efficiency. Compete with yourself to improve your times, refine your movement, and rise to the top of the speedrunning community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its sleek grid-based aesthetics, pulse-pounding soundtrack, and challenging parkour gameplay, <strong>HYPERLEAP</strong> offers a heart-pounding experience where precision, speed, and strategy determine victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take the leap?</p>",
